totalmente desnuda...

1585
01:59:02,215 --> 01:59:03,250
Simone.

1586
01:59:03,655 --> 01:59:04,804
¿Si, Edith?

1587
01:59:07,375 --> 01:59:08,854
No he rezado.

1588
